      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1485</offset>
        <text>In addition, members of uncharacterized lineages also responded.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">11</infon>
        <offset>1550</offset>
        <text>The MicroTOOLs microarray provides a robust tool for comprehensive characterization of major functional groups of microbes in the open ocean, and the design can be easily amended for specific environments and research questions.
</text>
